Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: This Human female was a Padawan who served the Jedi Order. As the Clone Wars was drawing to an end, she was inside the Jedi Temple's library when she witnessed Anakin Skywalker enter with two clone troopers. She watched in horror when Skywalker, who had turned to the dark side and became the Sith Lord Darth Vader, brutally murdered Jedi Master Jocasta Nu. Along with other Jedi in the room, she tried to avenge Nu's death, but was slain by Vader which led to the beginning of the Great Jedi Purge.
